{
  "texts": [
    "The challenge attracted 22 participating teams from academia and industry, accelerated research and generated discussion on this topic.",
    "Data and tracksThere were two tracks in the VoiceMOS Challenge 2022, namely the main track and the out-of-domain track.",
    "Table 1 summarizes the datasets.In 2021, we collected a large-scale dataset of MOS ratings for synthesized audio samples as well as reference natural speech samples.",
    "We gathered Englishlanguage synthesized audio samples from several past Blizzard Challenges from 2008-2016 [65,66,[128][129][130][131], as well as from all previous Voice Conversion Challenges [69][70][71].",
    "We also wanted to include samples from more recent systems, so we added publicly-shared samples from ESPnet-TTS [132]."
  ]
}